	(text_box "Volume control is made logrithmic by the sequence of diodes that modify the equivalent resistance as voltage increase. Volume control to LM13700 is current based. A pair of 4.7K resistors split from this note to each Iabc of the LM13700."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 210.82 75.9986 0)
		(size 35.56 18.2607)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
		(stroke
			(width 0)
